sortArray2 pseudo

sortArr(arr, size)

for InsertionSort ascending

for(i = 1; i < size; i++) //starting at 1, leaving space for insert
{
	max = A[i];
	int j = i;

	while(j > 0 && a[j-1] > max)
	{
		A[j] = a[j - 1]
		j = j - 1;
	}

	a[j] = max;
}

for InsertionSort descending


change while(j > 0 && a[j - 1] > max)

to 

while(j < 0 && a[j - 1] < max)

So instead of making sure that the larger terms move upward
and swap accordingly, we make sure that the smaller terms move
upward.	